{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>各位新手爸爸或需要時刻關注孩子成長的您，是否曾感到力不從心，錯過了與寶貝們的珍貴互動時光呢？現在，這款強大的親子提醒工具《Good Dad》將為您帶來轉變，它能精準解決您在日常育兒中面臨的挑戰，幫助您成為心中理想的父親形象，而現在正是您把握機會的最佳時機，因為它正限時免費提供下載。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-94.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>為您與全家人量身打造的貼心提醒</h2>\n    <p>《Good Dad》最核心的優勢在於其極致的個人化設定，無論您家中擁有一個或多個孩子，它都能為每一個孩子生成專屬的互動提示，包含輸入孩子的姓名與生日，App 便能客製化超過 100 則提醒，從關心孩子一天的生活到符合不同年齡層的引導，甚至還能自動通知生日，確保您不錯過任何重要的慶祝時刻。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-164-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-165-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-166-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-167-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-168-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-169-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Good Dad</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Lifestyle</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T20:02:10.128329+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":346,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}